Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.18,ZhuYin,,0,0,0,,PLAY the GAME!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,先和对方说话看看对方是否还有意识
