Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,现你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.21,0:20:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃离隧道！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！新来的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:20:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gatcha
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:20:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.75,0:21:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,学长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.33,0:21:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道没有那种回过神来身体已经先做出反应的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你在胡说些什么啊你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.65,0:21:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就是现在哟！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这才是英雄啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,失忆症效应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.39,ZhuYin,,0,0,0,,Amnesia Effect
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,等下！
